Phase 6 Part 4 - metrics.ts standalone verification
Command: node --experimental-transform-types run.ts
(run against a copy of the ACTUAL production file
backend/src/infrastructure/observability/metrics.ts, simulating 4 requests
through metricsMiddleware() then asserting on renderMetrics() output)

Result: 6/6 PASS
- PASS: has HELP lines
- PASS: has TYPE lines
- PASS: counts GET /payments/plans as 2
- PASS: has histogram bucket
- PASS: has +Inf bucket
- PASS: has memory metrics

Fix applied during this verification: metrics.ts imported
{ NextFunction, Request, Response } from "express" as a plain (non-type)
import. Under Node's --experimental-transform-types (no cross-file type
analysis), this fails at runtime with ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND since express
is not installed in this sandbox. Changed to `import type { ... }` --
correct either way under a real tsc build, and necessary for this
sandbox's file-execution verification method.
